        "text_FnPaY3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>A compromised skin barrier increases transepidermal water loss, leaving skin dry, reactive and more vulnerable to environmental stressors that contribute to sensitivity, fine lines and loss of elasticity.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://cantabrialabs.co.uk/collections/endocare-age-barrier\" title=\"Discover ENDOCARE AGE BARRIER products\"><strong>ENDOCARE AGE BARRIER</strong></a> combines hyaluronic acid, niacinamide and patented EDAFENCE® technology to restore hydration, strengthen barrier function and protect against pollution-induced oxidative stress for improved resilience and skin quality. </p>\n\n<p><b>Discover more about ENDOCARE AGE BARRIER Niacinal Serum Gel, clinically proven to show a +40% improvement in skin barrier function in 2 weeks and +24% hydration in 4 weeks.<sup>1</sup></b></p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_m6G4Db": {
