          }
        },
        "text_RPAUqp": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Oxidative stress from UV and pollution is a key driver of dullness, uneven tone and premature skin ageing. Ongoing free radical damage can disrupt skin clarity, contribute to dark spots and accelerate visible photoageing.</p>\n\n<p><b><a href=\"https://cantabrialabs.co.uk/collections/endocare-radiance\" title=\"Discover ENDOCARE RADIANCE products\">ENDOCARE RADIANCE</a></b> combines Vitamin C with Vitamin E, Ferulic Acid and patented EDAFENCE® technology to deliver high-efficacy antioxidant protection, defend against environmental stress and visibly brighten skin for improved clarity and luminosity.</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn more about ENDOCARE RADIANCE C Ferulic Serum Gel’s potent, clinically proven ingredients. In just 28 days, 80% of users saw softer, brighter, more radiant skin, 90% of users saw improved skin elasticity and 86% of users said skin was more nourished, hydrated and plump.<sup>2</sup></b></p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_rnpU3m": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
