      "blocks": {
        "heading_Y4DNc9": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Targeted cellular renewal for smoother, firmer-looking skin",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_aE8zB7": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>As cellular renewal slows with age and environmental stress, dull surface cells build up, texture becomes uneven and fine lines become more visible. Reduced turnover accelerates visible ageing and impacts skin clarity and firmness.</p>\n\n<p><b><a href=\"https://cantabrialabs.co.uk/collections/endocare-renewal\" title=\"Discover ENDOCARE RENEWAL products\">ENDOCARE RENEWAL</a></b> features retinoids strategically combined in unique RetinDuo® technology with AHAs and Azelaic Acid to support effective cellular turnover, refine texture and improve tone, helping restore smoother, clearer and more resilient-looking skin.</p>\n\n<p><b>Discover ENDOCARE RENEWAL Retinoid Intensive Serum, powered by RetinDuo® Technology combining 0.3% pure retinol and encapsulated retinal for intensified renewal with enhanced tolerability. Clinically tested, 90% of users reported more renewed, repaired and brighter skin, while 85% reported reduced fine lines and wrinkles.<sup>3</sup></b></p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_eBgBPL": {
